title: Malcolm Douglas - Australia [DUAL.Eng-Deu] Return To The Desert
description:
Malcolm Douglas - Return to the Desert (1979 - Australia)

Adventure / Travel / Documentary
 
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Malcolm_Douglas_(documentary_maker)


With a group of Kukadja men, Malcolm travels into the remote Great Sandy Desert of Western Australia. The desert tribesmen teach him their skills of survival, hunting and collecting. The amazing wildlife in the film includes rare footage of the tiny marsupial mole.

Malcolm Douglas (1941-2010) produced over 50 travel and adventure films for Australian television during the last 40 years. When Malcolm Douglas immersed himself within an Indigenous cultural landscape, he took lounge rooms full of Australian viewers with him.
